r":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/83/188332.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1550254","time":"2020-1-18 21:33","userId":"lostanother","userName":"Another","userSign":"(追番日益，补番日损)","message":"<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">小学借过同学的《你家里有镜子吗》看，当晚做噩梦<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/16.gif\" smileid=\"55\" alt=\"(bgm39)\"></span><br>原来想看长篇，斯蒂芬金的可以试试？（我只听过没看过<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/33/233376.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1550481","time":"2020-1-19 20:29","userId":"xhy24825","userName":"罪のM豆","userSign":"","message":"刚发现没有回复你<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/14.gif\" smileid=\"53\" alt=\"(bgm37)\"><br>其实小时候我感觉大多都是封面比较吓人啦，我现在读恐怖小说感觉还好，但是一到影像上就很难受了w"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/33/333373.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1550298","time":"2020-1-19 03:30","userId":"gracehuyelin","userName":"胡披萨","userSign":"(饮饕共舞)","message":"同楼上。斯蒂芬金的《故事贩卖机》，恐怖短篇小说集。收录的名作有《迷雾》等等。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/33/233376.jpg","floor":"#7-1","id":"1550352","time":"2020-1-19 11:13","userId":"xhy24825","userName":"罪のM豆","userSign":"","message":"史蒂芬金的话，我回头看看去<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/14.gif\" smileid=\"53\" alt=\"(bgm37)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/22/232238.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1550326","time":"2020-1-19 08:38","userId":"nutshell","userName":"NUTSHELL","userSign":"(il faut imaginer Sisyphe heureux)","message":"恐怖故事绝对属于厕所读物啊，这才有味道啊。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><br>推荐位国内作家吧：周德东，水平一般，中短篇为主，但是接国内地气。当年他主编了一本叫<span style=\"font-style:italic\">民间故事</span>的短篇恐怖小说杂志，水平相当可以。要是有兴趣可以淘来看看。<br><br>大名鼎鼎的蔡骏，当年风光一时，我个人倒不是很中意，也不妨看看。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/33/233376.jpg","floor":"#8-1","id":"1550353","time":"2020-1-19 11:14","userId":"xhy24825","userName":"罪のM豆","userSign":"","message":"谢推荐<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/14.gif\" smileid=\"53\" alt=\"(bgm37)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/83/128390.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1550341","time":"2020-1-19 10:16","userId":"128390","userName":"渐渐融化的飘雪","userSign":"","message":"每晚一个恐怖故事，基本都是单元剧，一共四本好像，还蛮有意思的。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/33/233376.jpg","floor":"#9-1","id":"1550356","time":"2020-1-19 11:15","userId":"xhy24825","userName":"罪のM豆","userSign":"","message":"谢谢啦<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/14.gif\" smileid=\"53\" alt=\"(bgm37)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/83/128390.jpg","floor":"#9-2","id":"1550547","time":"2020-1-20 06:41","userId":"128390","userName":"渐渐融化的飘雪","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">罪のM豆</span> 说: 谢谢啦</q></div>哦我昨天打错名字了，是《每晚一个离奇故事》，我昨天也打开读了几个故事，还算蛮有意思的，此外如果读漫画的话其实很多古早漫画都是这种恐怖单元剧的形式～"}]}]